      </div>
      <div class="decor_top_cube">
        <img src="/img/cube_3d.webp" alt="" width="82" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <div class="info_blk_home">
        <h1 class="heading_home">On-Demand <br><span class="blue_color">Design Services</span></h1>
        <div class="descr_home_fir">Ongoing design support or one-off projects at a price <br>that won't break the bank!</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 images_homm">
      <div class="item_im_gri" data-show-down-mobile data-delay=".1">
